high_descs: Turn left and walk around the toilet and then straight to the left most sink.
Open the bottom right cabinet and take out the green spray bottle.
Turn around and veer left around the toilet to the other side of it.
Place the spray bottle on the toilet tank on the bottom left corner.
Turn left and walk around the toilet tank again to the left sink.
Pick up the green spray bottle on the counter.
Turn around and veer left around the toilet to the other side of it.
Place the spray bottle on the toilet tank behind the other one.
anns.task_desc: Place two spray bottles on a toilet tank.

Turn completely around and walk forward a bit, then go to the toilet on the right. Face the toilet on the right side of it.
Put the green spray bottle on the back end of the toilet.
Make a left and walk halfway across the bathroom. Make a right turn and walk to the sink.
Pick up the green bottle next to the sink.
Turn around and walk forward a bit then go to the toilet on the right. Face the toilet on the right side of it.
Put the bottle on the back of the toilet next to the other green bottle.
anns.task_desc: Move two green spray bottles to the back of the toilet.
